              <text>Section 130(1)(b): omit <amend.in quote="1">Securities Commission</amend.in> and substitute <amend.in quote="1">Financial Markets Authority</amend.in>.</text>
            </para>
            <para>
              <text>Section 137(4) and (5): repeal and substitute:</text>
