            </para>
            <para>
              <text>Heading to section 101I: omit <amend.in quote="1"><emphasis style="bold">Government Actuary's</emphasis></amend.in> and substitute <amend.in quote="1"><emphasis style="bold">FMA's</emphasis></amend.in>.</text>
