            </para>
            <para>
              <text>Section 101I(7): omit <amend.in quote="1">Government Actuary's</amend.in> and substitute <amend.in quote="1">FMA's</amend.in>.</text>
            </para>
            <para>
              <text>Section 134(1): omit <amend.in quote="1">Government Actuary</amend.in> in each place where it appears and substitute in each case <amend.in quote="1">FMA</amend.in>.</text>
            </para>
            <para>
              <text>Section 134(1)(a): omit <amend.in quote="1">he or she</amend.in> and substitute <amend.in quote="1">the FMA</amend.in>.</text>
            </para>
            <para>
              <text>Section 134(2): omit <amend.in quote="1">Government Actuary</amend.in> and substitute <amend.in quote="1">FMA</amend.in>.</text>
            </para>
            <para>
              <text>Heading to section 137: omit <amend.in quote="1"><emphasis style="bold">Government Actuary</emphasis></amend.in> and substitute <amend.in quote="1"><emphasis style="bold">FMA</emphasis></amend.in>.</text>
            </para>
            <para>
              <text>Section 137(1): omit <amend.in quote="1">Government Actuary</amend.in> in each place where it appears and substitute in each case <amend.in quote="1">FMA</amend.in>.</text>
