                    <text><def-term id="DLM3232406">FMA</def-term> means the Financial Markets Authority established under <changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">Part 2</citation></changeable> of the <changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">Financial Markets (Regulators and KiwiSaver) Act 2010</citation></changeable></text>
                  </para>
