                    <text>in respect of a document, information, or other matter required to be made publicly available under <changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">section 54C</citation></changeable> of the Act that is an advertisement only by reason of <changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">section 2A(2)(c)</citation></changeable> of the Act:</text>
