              <amend increment="1" quote="1">
                <label-para quote="1" skeleton="no">
                  <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">g</label>
                  <para>
                    <text>in relation to an interest in a KiwiSaver scheme other than a restricted KiwiSaver scheme, or to an advertisement, investment statement, prospectus, or registered prospectus that relates to such an interest, the manager of the scheme</text>
                  </para>
